{
  "stem": "1222.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Water, we used to drink from little ditches, wherever it was a little water to get.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Dirt-- we were full, pardon my expression, with lice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Lice was all over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I used to take in all over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were very filthy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But God saved me from that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't have [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's why [SOBBING] I believe that must be somebody miracle happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was-- I wasn't made smart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If I would be smart, maybe I would-- maybe I should have gone with the parents to go to the grave.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So probably, I was mean that way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was selfish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I still say I don't deserve anything, but probably somebody wants I should do it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was right there in the forest, right there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walked into our small little town--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mezhyrich.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mezhyrich.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we took away a big house, and we were probably approximately just about 30 partisans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were standing there-- we were sleeping right on the floor together with the partisans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a child at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was 15.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't feel any discriminating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They knew that I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They used to call me [NON-ENGLISH], that means son.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when they had the food, they had the food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They would not share the food, because they used to go into the farmers-- they didn't give them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They used to kill them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they used to give me the best food, because they wanted to bring me-- I should be healthy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't feel-- they were very nice to me, but you had to obey it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "A lot of the children, they had to go to the-- to the-- you know, in the ditches to put away a pail, and it used to blow up many times.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Fortunately, I was too young.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
